latestIgtvVideos.title: TERI MITTI
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
All days are not special but some days make you feel simply happy .When I look back to this day, It is probably one of the best days of my life 
I remember me being nervous and excitement I felt through my bones a day before this workshop as it was my first 
and this song is really close to my heart ideally don't want to choreograph this song because confused about not giving justice to it as it is beautiful song cover by @parineetichopra
but then I also just wanted to do go for it and hope my efforts came across well 
but all this couldn't be possible without many people around me firstly my all  mentors for the knowledge , support and advice also biggest thankyou to ❤️❤️@karan.bigdance @atulbigdance @akankshabhakoo for believing in me 
Thankyou so much @bigdancecentre ❤️ also a big thankyou to people who helped me go through all the problems I had during this
and very special and huge thankyou to people who came for the workshop and supported me
thankyou so much couldn't have done this without you guys 
thankyou so much for your love ❤️❤️, felt really blessed nd emotional 
Song- teri Mitti by @parineetichopra ❤️❤️

latestPosts.caption:
Nothing matches the feeling of representing your country on a global platform 🇮🇳✨
And I’m blessed I got this opportunity through @iccr_delhi (Indian Council of Cultural Relations) to feel it through my art and promote our precious beautiful culture in abroad 
I realised how the arts can inspire, connect, and celebrate the beauty of shared traditions
It’s an honour to perform in front of the top dignitaries/Ministers of Mauritius,Malaysia 
 @igcic.mauritius @hcimauritius  @nscbicc @hci_kualalumpur @ministryofculturegoi @meaindia 
 
Sometimes Victory is within grasp if you believe oneself to achieve lucid dreams manifest heartfelt 
The experience of holding my first white/official Passport in hand 
Something I manifested from the early days when I was preparing for upsc 
But achieving it all through my art is overwhelming
 
And in the process met some beautiful people to spend time and share the memories with 
@_allabout.vishal_ @kashikabassi @sparkingmonika @anand_journey @raut1282 @nritya_artravi @khushibari__ @ashish_dance7 
Without you guys it wouldn’t be easier .Thankyouuuu so muchhhh 🫶🏽😘
And thanks to Ajay sir for this opportunity 

Grateful and thankful to the universe for all the blessings 
Indeed best start to the year 2025 🧿✨
JAI HIND 🇮🇳
